Xdriller is a Mr.Driller clone. This program is released under the 
GPLv3 license (see COPYING file).

This is a continuation of the original Fixi Studios codebase with
updates removing old libraries.

BUILD REQUIRES:

- CMAKE
- gettext
- Ogre 14
- OIS
- tinyxml2
- sdl2
- sdl2_mixer

INSTRUCTIONS:

mkdir build
cmake ..
make

./xdriller

to install:

sudo make install

to uninstall:

sudo make uninstall

to remove config files type:

rm ~/.config/xdriller -R

